NAME
    padre-brew.pl

VERSION
    version 0.01

SYNOPSIS
    perl padre-brew.pl -v
    perl padre-brew.pl -v --no-test

DESCRIPTION
    CURRENTLY ONLY RUNS ON OSX!
    
    This script will eventually become a package to create standalone packages/directories of Padre.
    
    Currently, on OSX, this script will create a PadreApp directory (default name) in the current
    directory that has a self-contained Padre and perl (32 bit).

    Take a look at the script for all command line arguments.
